stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> CLOSED
  CLOSED --> RECOVERY_RUNNING: startup enters recovery
  RECOVERY_RUNNING --> READ_ONLY_DIAGNOSTIC: force validation mode
  READ_ONLY_DIAGNOSTIC --> CLOSED: validation complete
  RECOVERY_RUNNING --> BACKGROUND_STARTING: required recovery stages complete
  BACKGROUND_STARTING --> OPEN: workers registered
  OPEN --> DRAINING_FOR_SHUTDOWN: shutdown requested
  DRAINING_FOR_SHUTDOWN --> CLOSED: sessions drained
  RECOVERY_RUNNING --> FAILED_CLOSED: recovery error
  FAILED_CLOSED --> CLOSED: admin restart
  OPEN --> [*]
